Text.string: So here's the DEAL! I'm holding an Atlas soldier HOSTAGE... but I'll exchange her if you FREE my girl Bloodshine! The cop bots got her, and they got her locked up in some stupid JAIL!
And don't screw with me! You screw with me and I kill the hostage and myself and a bunch of other people! 'Cause I'm in LOVE! And INSANE!
You wipe out the copbots yet? If anything happens to Bloodshine, I'm gonna murder your whole family... AND this old man I know with a pet gopher... and the gopher! 'Cause I'm IN LOVE!
T-head, baby? You send some grunts to save me? I'm over here!
Saved by a Vault Thief? Bloodshine ain't no Vault Hunter lover! I'm gonna offer your spleen to Tyreen!
Ghhahahagahahagahagahhhhh!
You find my baby Bloodshine yet? Light of my LIFE, tumor in my EYE?
Yup. Her heart is all... yours.
Uh, yes! And she can't wait to put her arms around you.
I have acquired your kidnapped girlfriend... parts.
I did! I... did. And she's... bloody excited to see you.
If Tumorhead finds out you killed Bloodshine, I'm a goner. But I've got an idea. Grab her mask.
See, Tumorhead's eyesight is crap. On account of the tumor, I'm guessing. Maybe we can fool her. See ya back at the hideout.
En route with Bloodshine.
Bloodshine and I are heading back.
Bloodshine and I return!
Me and Bloodshine are on our way.
GOOOOOOD! Bring her back to my place. Then we'll swap prisoners!

Vault Hunter. I'm Naoko, Tumorhead's prisoner. But I'm not an Atlas soldier like she thinks. If she finds out who I really am, I'm a goner. Thanks for trying to rescue me, but it looks like we'll have to do what she says and play along for now. Help me get out of here and I'll tell you everything.
Hey. Don't feel bad for Bloodshine. These two are in love with killing innocent civilians. They're monsters.. Plus, PDA is gross. I mean, seriously, grow up. No one wants to see that!
Thanks for taking out those cop bots, whoever you are. Are you here for the EXCHANGE?! Come talk to me.
Bloodshine! SWEETY?! You here? I can SMELL ya, baby! Come on in!
Get ready.
Surprise! I want you to be my broodmate... for LIFE! And your mom's here with me to celebrate!
Whaddaya want out there?! State yer business!
Yeah! We got some murders about to happen out here.
I think there might be some murders out here in a few seconds.
There are many crimes about to be committed. By me.
Right. I've gotta report a buncha murders that are about to happen.
Oh, you think you're some kinda funny, don'tcha? I'll teach ya some manners!
Well, that... sorta worked. At least you got in. We'll talk after the bloodbath.
Vault Hunter, help!
Okay, now put Bloodshine's mask on one of the dead bodies by the door. That should be enough to fool them into letting you in.
Welcome back!
Welcome BACK!
I gotta disappear for a while. Most people around here would kill me just for my last name. But if you see my brother, put a bullet in that dickbag's head for me.
Oh, and Tumorhead stole a family heirloom of mine. I don't want it anymore, so it's all yours, Vault Hunter. No offense, but I hope I never see you again. Seriously.
Surprise!
Congratulations!
Hooray for LOVE!
She's dead! She's DEAD!
The Vault Thief killed Bloodshine!
Blood feud!
Now that that Tumorhead maniac is dead, get me out of here!
Way ahead of you.
Already done.
I have already done that.
Job's already done, girl!
Now that you got me out, it's time to tell you that my full name is Naoko... Katagawa. Yeah. My dickbag brother had all my siblings murdered by Tyreen Calypso. I'm the only one left.
Oh. Good. That's... yeah, screw that guy.
Welcome back, baby!
Welcome BACK, BABY!
As soon as I realized what my brother was doing, I tried to disappear on Promethea—found a dead Atlas soldier and stole his gear. Then I got captured by the COV.
Come here and let me thank you for getting me out.
We know you've got a hostage in there, and we want a cut of the ransom! Now open up!
Hey, you! You ain't takin' our cut. Get 'em, boys!

Why did you do this to ME?! You killed my BABY! And her MOM! And her BEST FRIEND! And her BROTHER AND her SISTER! And my whole freakin' CREW! You took everything from us! We were gonna start a taco truck together! I WILL DESTROY YOU!

If you can hear this, I need your help. I've been taken prisoner by this COV lunatic named Tumorhead. She wants to set up a prisoner exchange for her girlfriend, Bloodshine. She thinks I'm an Atlas soldier, but I'm not. If you help me, I'll make it worth your while, seriously. Head down to her hideout. It's down in the subway tunnels.
Just so you know, I'm not like my brother. Dude's a psychopath, and he DEFINITELY wants me dead.
On approach to the copbot HQ.
I'm at the copbot HQ.
The copbot HQ nears.
Nearing the copbot HQ.
Now, find a way to get inside and SMASH those copbots! Then free my baby Bloodshine!
